column5: Will be going to O'sullivan Rainbow 7/24/2010. Please reply with fishing reports from your trips, this year. We have been fishing O'Sullivan for 17 years and I would be willing to share information with any one fishing the lake for the first time.
Going there for week of July 10. Will post report upon return. Bill Krejca
Great!!! Thanks for the reply and good luck. Tell Bob and Shelly that we are looking forward to it. ( I am with the Don Rauch group. )
It's only been 15 years and you still can't fish. Check out the recipes on this site. Sounds like we should try a couple new ones.
